Emacs Configuration
===================

To use this configuration:

1. update git submodules in src/

  $ git submodule init
  $ git submodule update

I'm using the development version of org-mode and Gnus, so this step
might take a while to complete.

You're adviced to compile at least Gnus:

  $ cd src/gnus/
  $ ./configure && make  # DON'T INSTALL IT! DON'T!!


2. Create a symbolic link in your HOME directory

  $ cd ~/
  $ ln -s THIS_CHECKOUT .emacs.d


3. Start Emacs and have fun
